      "date": "2018-08-13 22:26:36.000000000",
      "message": "Abandoned\n\nAbandon this patch in favour of https://review.whamcloud.com/8201 which has all of the review history.  You should be able to push an updated version of the patch by using\n\n Change-Id: Ia004d6b39272df8159c9df3cc76662e198230b55 \n\n> The 'parallel' here means to issue I/O to different stripes\n> simultaneously. It's confusing since we have had some other\n> 'parallel I/O' unfortunately. I changed 'parallel' IO to\n> lockless I/O in my patch though.\n\nThis should be included into the patch commit description.",
